To run a local copy, make a .env file with the following info (change variables as necessary):

DB_HOST="localhost"
DB_USER="root"
DB_PASSWORD="password"
DB_NAME="api_assignment"
PORT=3306

To install required packages, run:
npm install

To run the code, run:
node server.js

The test script uses mocha, which needs to be installed beforehand. To do this, run:
npm install --global mocha

To run the test, run:
mocha test/test.js
